templateData.information: At Execyoution, we value your privacy and desire in knowing how information about you is collected and used. This privacy policy governs the manner in which Execyoution Inc. (“Execyoution” or “we“) collects, maintains, uses and discloses information collected from users (each, a “user”) of our websites and/or chatbots. This privacy policy applies to all sites (including execyoution.com and 1min.me) and all products and services offered at Execyoution.com, 1min.me and our 1min.me Facebook Messenger chatbot (our “sites” or “site“).
